#Latitude
N 65-50: UK, Nordics, Russia, Germany, Poland
N 50-35: USA, France, Spain, Italy, Balcan, Turkey, China, Japan
N 35-20: USA, Mexico, Maghreb, Mashrek, Iran, India, China
N 20-0: Venezuela, West Africa, Horn of Africa, Indochina, Philippines
S 0-20: Peru, Brazil, Congo, African Great Lakes, Indonesia
S 20-35: Brazil, Argentina, South Africa, Australia
S 35-50: New Zealand

#Timezones
UTC: UK, Ireland, Portugal, Iceland
+1: Europe (most), Morocco, Algeria, Tunis
+2: Finland, Baltics, Ukraine, Romania, Bulgaria, Greece, Egypt, South Africa
+3: Russia (Moscow), Turkey, Saudi Arabia
+3.5: Iran
+5.5: India
+7: Thailand, Vietnam
+8: China, Malaysia, Philippines, west Australia
+9: Korea, Japan
+10: east Australia
+12: New Zealand
-8: west USA
-6: Texas, Chicago, Mexico (most)
-5: east USA, Colombia, Peru
-3: Brazil (most), Argentina, Chile

