#Ethnics
Afghanistan: 50% Pashtuns, 30% Tajiks, 10% Hazaras, 10% Uzbeks
Iran: 60% Persians, 15% Azeris, 10% Kurds
Kazakhstan: 70% Kazakh, 15% Russian
Kyrgyzstan: 75% Kyrgyz, 15% Uzbeks
Pakistan: 45% Punjabis, 20% Pashtuns, 15% Sindhis, 10% Saraikis
Turkey: 75% Turks, 20% Kurds
